entries.journal_entry_description: Yraka Nes, the medical nurse of the Myyydril encampment, needs your help in collecting 20 Webweaver Strands for blankets. The blankets are used to soothe the "afflicted" and are very important to Yraka.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Collect 20 Webweaver Strands from the webweavers in the Kkowir Forest.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Bring the blankets back to Yraka Nes.
